Latest completed work (archived purge + marker attribution correctness)
- Added permanent cleanup action in `Admin Data Tools`:
  - `Permanently Delete Archived` (selected archived markers only)
  - Two-step safety confirmation (`confirm` + type `DELETE`)
  - Deletes from Firestore for cloud markers and removes local-only archived markers from session state.
- Fixed marker attribution in engagement mode so building/floor context is only attached when valid:
  - Campus scope: marker gets `buildingId/buildingName` only when click lands on a building footprint.
  - Floor scope: marker gets `building/floor/room` context only when click lands inside the loaded floorplan geometry.
  - Outside-building clicks no longer inherit the Floorplans panel selection, preventing false `buildingId/buildingName` assignment.

